      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着向那被他砍死的大汉一指，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着哈哈大笑。札木合道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她手中长剑却已给柯镇恶铁杖砸飞。柯镇恶出声长叹，铁杖重重一顿，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ke_zhen_e",
      "speaker_name": "柯镇恶",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "教你内功的那人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他他⋯⋯他⋯⋯在外面，求见六位师父。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱聪仍紧紧抓住郭靖手腕不放，只点头为礼，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "忙抢着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是全真教马钰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他⋯⋯他叫我不要说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是，是道长。",
