      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "道士伯伯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "道长",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶适才险些伤了他性命，心下甚是歉疚，对这徒儿更增怜爱，只怕他走开之后，竟遇上了梅超风而受到伤害，忙道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "抽噎噎的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爹爹要我，要我就去嫁给那个都史⋯⋯",
      "tone": "悲伤",
