      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 960,
      "line_end": 960
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "札木合道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 962,
      "line_end": 962
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁木真道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 964,
      "line_end": 964
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "札木合道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 966,
      "line_end": 966
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁木真深知桑昆和札木合的为人，要是落入他二人手中，必然无幸，倘若王罕亲自领军，投降后或尚有活命之望，举刀在空中呼的一声，劈了一刀，厉声叫道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 968,
      "line_end": 968
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁木真厉声道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 976,
      "line_end": 976
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "札木合道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
