      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1094,
      "line_end": 1094
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两句话他学了已久，这时第一次才对人说，危急之中，居然并未忘记，只是把",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1096,
      "line_end": 1096
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "探海斩蛟",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1106,
      "line_end": 1106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "翻身探果",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1110,
      "line_end": 1110
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进步提篮",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1120,
      "line_end": 1120
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "了头皮问",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "六位可是江南六怪么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1174,
      "line_end": 1174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1176,
      "line_end": 1176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "使双斧的抚着小腹上给郭靖踹中之处，怒道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1182,
      "line_end": 1182
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柯镇恶道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1186,
      "line_end": 1186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "钱青健问马青雄道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1194,
      "line_end": 1194
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果听铁木真道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1246,
      "line_end": 1246
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着右手从胸口衣内伸了出来，满手都是鲜血，又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1248,
      "line_end": 1248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ji_si_han",
      "speaker_name": "铁木真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "监禁起来，三日之后，全家斩首。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1258,
      "line_end": 1258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸将相顾愕然，铁木真道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1266,
      "line_end": 1266
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "下令将五名亲兵在札木合之前斩下首级，转头对札木合道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1292,
      "line_end": 1292
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "札木合流泪道：",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1294,
      "line_end": 1294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁木真黯然良久，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1296,
      "line_end": 1296
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "成吉思汗",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1304,
      "line_end": 1304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_ji_si_han",
      "speaker_name": "成吉思汗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我把华筝给你，从明天起，你是我的金刀驸马。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1314,
      "line_end": 1314
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当下把亡夫昔年与义弟杨铁心指腹为婚之事说了，最后道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1336,
      "line_end": 1336
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李萍又惊又喜，忙问：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1344,
      "line_end": 1344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ping",
      "speaker_name": "李萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朱聪道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1344,
      "line_end": 1344
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1370,
      "line_end": 1370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_lei",
      "speaker_name": "拖雷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妹子，你跟他说话啊！我不听就是。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1387,
      "line_end": 1387
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖点头，问道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1391,
      "line_end": 1391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我要去了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 1393,
      "line_end": 1393
    }
